I want to study social work to help children who are hurt or not taken care of. I also want to help families who are having problems. Important things I can bring to the social work field are service, respect, and a strong sense of right and wrong. I want to help people and myself become better at our jobs.

I have always wanted to help others, but I did not know what job was right for me. In school, I saw people try to escape their problems and use bad ways to deal with them. I got a degree in Psychology from Piedmont College in 2009, but I still did not know what I wanted to do. One summer, a friend introduced me to a 16-year-old boy who was running away from his bad home life. The next day, he called the police. I went to his home and talked to the police. I told them I had a degree in Psychology and could talk to the parents. I asked them about the boy's situation, but they made excuses for his behavior. After this, I started thinking seriously about a career in social work to help kids with family problems.

A very important thing in social work is fairness for everyone. We say that each person is special and we feel sad when someone dies. But we try to be like everyone else instead of being unique. I do not like following what others do. In school, I spoke out against unfairness whenever I could: I colored my hair in different colors, wore clothes that showed my personality, and stood up for the rights of everyone, including people who are gay, black, and against racism and unfair treatment. I believe in fairness and will keep fighting for it.

This paper talks about two ways to look at insomnia. One way is the biological model. This model looks at genetics and medical health. The other way is the sociocultural model. This model looks at how the environment, like where you live and how much money you make, affects your sleep.

The biological model finds out how genes and the body work together to cause insomnia. The brain has special cells that help us sleep and wake up. These cells are called orexin. Scientists studied mice and found that these cells work with a special receiver called GABAB. When the GABAB receiver is active, it helps us sleep. If it is not working well, we may have trouble sleeping.

A study on mice showed that a special medicine called baclofen can help us sleep. This means that the human body and brain work in a similar way to the mice. The study found that a problem with the GABAB receiver can cause insomnia. This means that some people may not be able to sleep well without medicine.

This study has sociocultural implications. If a person inherits a problem with the GABAB receiver, they may have trouble sleeping. This can affect their life in many ways, such as school, work, and daily tasks.

Insomnia can be caused by many things, including other mental health problems. It can also be caused by medical problems or by taking certain substances. There are different types of insomnia, including primary insomnia, which is trouble falling asleep or staying awake. Hypersomnia is trouble staying awake. Narcolepsy is a condition that makes us fall asleep suddenly.

There are two types of sleep disorders: Dyssomnias and Parasomnias. Dyssomnias are trouble falling asleep or staying asleep. Parasomnias are sleep disorders that cause abnormal behavior or physical problems while we are sleeping.

This paper talks about Central Auditory Processing Disorder, or CAPD. CAPD is a disorder that affects how the brain uses sound information. It means the brain cannot properly understand what we hear. People with CAPD can hear normally, but they have trouble understanding speech and background noise.

The first mention of CAPD was in the 1950s. Since then, researchers have been studying the disorder. A team of Italian researchers started developing tests for children with CAPD in 1954. In 1961, another researcher, Kimura, created a test to understand how the brain processes sound.

People with CAPD have trouble with many things. They may not be able to tell where a sound is coming from. They may have trouble hearing two or more sounds at the same time. They may not be able to understand sound patterns or changes in speech. They may also have trouble understanding what they hear when one sound is covered by another sound.

To diagnose CAPD, doctors use observation and tests. They may ask questions and watch how the patient responds to different sounds. There is no one test that works for everyone. Doctors use different tests to see how the patient's brain processes sound. These tests can include asking the patient to choose between different sounds or words. More advanced tests use special equipment to record sound signals and see how the brain responds.

The play Twelfth Night shows that wearing a disguise is useful for tricking people, but in the end, it can lead to problems. A person who wears a disguise may lose themselves in the process. Ending a deception is hard because it can cause people to feel left out or angry.

A big problem with wearing a disguise is that it can hurt relationships with others. People may not be happy when they find out they were tricked. Some may be angry and not want to be friends with the person who tricked them.

The play talks about a person wearing a disguise to change their sex. This is a big problem. It raises many questions, like "Why do people want to change their sex?" In Twelfth Night, a woman named Viola wants to be a man. She wants to protect herself from people who might hurt her. Viola's plan works, but it also makes it hard for her to be friends with other women.

Viola's disguise makes it hard for her to be honest about her feelings. She falls in love with a woman named Olivia, but Olivia thinks Viola is a man. Viola also likes a man named Orsino, but she does not know how to tell him how she feels. 

The play shows that wearing a disguise can help people figure out their true feelings. Olivia and Orsino may have feelings for each other, but they do not know it. When Viola appears as a man, it makes them think about their feelings. But this is not the only reason for Olivia's behavior. Olivia is a strong woman who judges people by their character, not their sex.

This is shown when Olivia quickly changes her mind about who she loves. She starts to think of Viola as a sister, not a lover.

The German government controlled many lands in Africa. This control was often very bad. Many people died in these lands. The Ovaherero and Nama people were especially hurt. 

The German government controlled many lands. Each land had different rules. The German government also controlled many different kinds of lands. 

Some African people in one land, East Africa, were educated. They could read and write. The German government helped some African people in other lands, like Kamerun. 

But another land, South West Africa, was different. The government did not help many African people learn. Instead, Christian groups helped. The government gave them some money, but not much. The government did help white people in the land. They built schools for the white people. This made a big difference in the way white people and African people lived.

Today, we know that many African people in South West Africa did not learn to read or write. Many people did not have an education. This happened because of many reasons. We will study these reasons in this paper. We will look at what white people and government leaders thought about African people.

There are many books about the German government's education system in Africa. Most of these books are in German and were written a long time ago. These books say how the education system worked in different lands. Later, people wrote more books in English. They compared education in different lands and looked at specific parts of the education system. These books show that the education systems in different lands were very different.

One important book is by Cohen. He compared the education systems in South West Africa and East Africa. He said that the number of white people in South West Africa was the reason for many differences in the education system.

South West Africa had a good climate. But most of the land was desert. Many white people lived in South West Africa. In 1913, there were 15,000 white people. This was more than in any other land controlled by Germany.

Popular music has many different kinds. Over 100 years, the number of kinds of popular music has grown very much. It is hard to make a list of all kinds. Most kinds of music have smaller kinds inside them. For example, rock music has many kinds like heavy metal, country music has many kinds, and so on.

Heavy metal music is one kind of rock music. It is very expressive. It shows many emotions, but it usually shows darker emotions. It is also very diverse. Many people like it because it is flexible. They can make their own kind of heavy metal music. Many kinds of heavy metal music have grown up. It is hard to say what heavy metal music is.

Heavy metal music has many different themes. It has taken ideas from other kinds of music. But it started from somewhere. To understand heavy metal music, we need to know what it is and why it exists.

Heavy metal music is often a music of more. It has more bass, more volume, more violence, and more drama. People in heavy metal bands know how to play their instruments well. They make good music. Heavy metal music is also connected to drugs. Some people used drugs to make music in the 1970s. They made crazy and unusual music. Heavy metal music has many dark and emotional qualities. It was new and different when it first came out. Later, other kinds of music took some of these qualities.

Some songs have dark and emotional lyrics. These lyrics show the darker side of music. One example is the song "Helter Skelter" by the Beatles. It is considered one of the first heavy metal songs. It was a response to another song by the Rolling Stones. The Beatles wanted to show that they could be as heavy as the Stones.

Many years before the Surrealist artists made famous works of art, a man named Henri Rousseau painted his own special pictures. His 1910 painting, The Dream, shows a woman who sees the beauty of a land in a dream. But The Dream also shows Rousseau's own dreams and hopes as an artist. He wanted people to like and understand his art. This was not easy for him. 

Rousseau had a big decision to make. He could try to paint like other famous artists to get approval from the art world, or he could be himself and paint what he wanted. This was a big choice for him.

To understand The Dream, you need to know a little about Rousseau's life. He was born in France on May 21, 1844. His father was a man who sold metal objects. Rousseau did not go to school to learn art. Instead, he worked in a town until he was 40 years old. He then started painting to make himself happy. 

Rousseau's first wife and their eight baby children died. He was left with only one daughter and much sadness. He wanted a new life, so he started painting. Unlike other artists, Rousseau painted about everyday life. He wanted to show what people like him saw and felt.

Rousseau wanted the art world to like his work. This was difficult because he was not trained in art like other painters. Many other famous artists made art at the same time as Rousseau. One of these artists was a man named Matisse. A book about French painters says that Rousseau and Matisse were different. Matisse wanted to make art in a special way to be different. Rousseau wanted to make art that was common, so people would understand and like it.

Many great thinkers believe that ethics and beauty are connected. I agree with them. John Keats said, "Beauty is truth. Truth is beauty." We learn many things in life from education and experience. But we also know that some things are beautiful or good without being taught. Ethics and aesthetics try to describe, not tell us what to do. We try to explain why art is beautiful or why an action is good, not make rules for judging good art or behavior.

We can't fully understand why something is good or beautiful by criticizing it. Talking about a great work of art, like da Vinci's Mona Lisa, can focus on details like color or background, but these don't explain why it's good. When people talk about their favorite art, they often say, "There's just something about it." This is true for both art and ethics. A story can't fully be explained with words. It's like Flannery O'Connor said, "We tell stories because words alone are not enough."

I think ethics and art have something in common. They can't be fully described. As Wittgenstein said, "Ethics is beyond words." I believe that this "something" is what makes art and morality special. This "something" connects ethics and aesthetics.

We experience ethics and art most deeply at a level that's hard to explain. This is especially true for literature. Literature is special because it has a moral quality. As McKean said, "Literature is important because it teaches us values."

Germany today is a strong country with its own culture. This culture is from the Alps to the Baltic Sea. It is the same culture in cities like München, Kiel, Köln, and Dresden. 

Germany has a special culture because it is made from different groups. 

The land where the Germans live is called Germania. We do not know for sure where the name "German" came from. Some think it is from a tribe called the Tungrians. Others think it is from a word used by the Gauls. 

The Gauls used the word "Germanus" to talk about the people who lived across the Rhine River. These people often fought the Gauls. 

One famous man, Julius Caesar, wrote about these people. He said they were always at war with the Gauls. He got the word "German" from the Gauls. 

Some people think the word "German" comes from a spear called a "ger". Others think it comes from an old Irish word "garim", which means "to shout". This means the Germans were loud.

A long time ago, a man named Tacitus wrote about the Germans. He said they were an old people who did not mix with other groups. They came to Germany on ships, not by land. He thought it was a hard place to live.

The Romans were not interested in living in Germany. They only went there to get things and fight battles. They would go back to their big empire when they were finished.

The Germanic tribes lived near the Roman Empire. They traded goods and skills with the Romans. They also served in the Roman army.

I looked down. My mind was empty. I did not think about what I saw. I just looked. Many thoughts came and went quickly. I was not thinking. I was just looking.

I read a book on art. It helped artists see better. I wanted to learn to draw when I was six years old. The book teaches how to understand lines and pictures. The book says to put a square around any picture. This makes the picture easier to see.

I looked at a bowl of fruit. I could not see a square around it. I was amazed. I stood there and looked. Many artists paint beautiful pictures. Picasso liked blue. Monet liked green. I wanted to make a good picture. I called it Work in Brown.

My hand moved to a pencil. I wanted to draw. My hand moved to the toilet. It was hard to move. The brown package would not go away.

I held a mop and looked at the package. I was unhappy. I wanted to clean it. I flushed the toilet many times. I stood still for a moment. Then I grabbed the toilet paper and wrapped my hand. I slowly put my hand in the bowl. It was hard to do.

Many young drivers are dying in car accidents. Experts say several things come together to cause this problem. The National Institutes of Health explain that young brains are not ready for the dangers of driving. Young drivers also have little experience behind the wheel. This lack of experience causes many accidents and makes it more likely for cars to roll over or drive off the road.

Teenagers often drive with their friends. Studies show that this is a big problem. When teenagers drive with friends, they are more likely to be in accidents. One study found that the age of the passenger and the number of accidents are connected.

California and other states have tried to make driving safer for young drivers. They have rules that limit the hours young drivers can drive and say they cannot have passengers under a certain age. However, these rules are not enough. Many experts think that young drivers are not ready to drive safely.

Psychologist Marvin Zuckerman says 18 is too young to get a driver's license. He says that people who are under 20 like to take risks. This makes sense. Many young people like to do things that give them a thrill. If we let young teens drive, we will see many more accidents. Many more people will die.

By 2010, many more young drivers will be on the road. This will make the problem worse. We need a new law to help solve this problem. The law would say that no one under 18 can drive. People under 18 could still learn to drive, but they could not drive alone. They would need to practice with a licensed driver. This would make the roads safer for everyone.

This idea is not new. Many states already have rules like this. A national law would be a good way to make sure all states follow the same rules. This would help keep young drivers safe everywhere.

I looked at the Library of Congress's film collection. The collection has 15 films from 1895 to 1901. These films use tricks to create illusions. I studied these films to understand their style and how they changed over time.

Most trick films are set in one place and do not move the camera. They use long shots and some medium shots. The camera does not move from its fixed position. The idea for these films came from the theater and magic shows. 

The set is like a stage. Actors move from side to side, but never towards or away from the camera. In one film, 'Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel,' actors enter from one side and move back and forth. They go out of the frame, but the camera does not follow them.

Most trick films show the actors from a distance. They do not use close-up shots. This is because the audience sees the whole performance, like in a theater. Actors do not move towards the camera, so close-ups are not possible.

Each trick film usually has one idea or one trick. This makes the films short, about a minute or less. Most trick films show simple tricks like magic and disappearing acts. However, some trick films can be more complex. They show how something appears or disappears. In the film 'The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots,' a close look shows when the "head" appears. The whole film seems like one shot, but it is actually made up of many small shots.

John Taylor was an important person in the early United States. He believed in individual freedom and was a strong supporter of the Republican Party. He thought that farming was the best kind of work. Taylor's ideas about farming and his short time in politics made him a well-known person who spoke his mind about the government and personal freedom.

Taylor thought that the United States had a good chance to create a perfect system of government. This was because the country did not have any old traditions to follow. He believed in the basic rights of all people, like freedom and fairness. He thought that if one of these rights is taken away, all the rights are not as good. Taylor said that the government should not have the power to take away these rights.

Taylor believed in a system where some people are good and some are bad. He thought that government should be fair and honest. He said that government is run by people, so it will have both good and bad qualities. He wanted a government that protects private property and helps farmers. He also wanted a government that does not let big business control everything.

Taylor believed in following the Constitution closely. He thought that the government should not have too much power. He wanted the government to only have the powers that the Constitution says it can have. Taylor did not want a big government because it would be expensive and could be mean. He also thought that if we only follow the words of the Constitution, it could be unfair. He thought the Declaration of Independence was more important because it said the United States is a group of independent states.

We look at Figure 17. There is a big drop in commuter log submissions in the third month of the project. This is somewhat disappointing. We do not know why this happens. In winter, people do not ride bicycles or walk as much. This might be one reason for the drop. Many students are busy in December. They have schoolwork and exams. They may forget to fill out the log. December is also the start of the holiday season. Students and teachers do not need to go to school. Classes start again in late January. But the number of log submissions is still low in February. One idea is that people are excited at first, but then they lose interest. We created a Carpool Challenge Week in March. This is a special event to get people to participate again. It worked and more people filled out the log that month.

Another problem is that people like driving their cars. This is a part of our culture. We need to make people want to use other ways to travel. We gave out prizes like gift cards to restaurants and stores. We wanted to see if bigger prizes would work better. For example, a new bicycle or a new car might make people want to participate more. The prizes did not change during the project. If we had given out bigger prizes, like a new bicycle or a new car, people might have been more interested. The gift cards were good at first, but bigger prizes might have helped.

An ETF is a type of investment.  It is a security that follows a group of stocks or a product, like an index fund.  But it is more flexible and can be bought and sold like a stock.  An ETF gives you the advantage of owning many stocks and the benefits of owning one stock.  You can sell it short, buy it on credit, and buy one share at a time.

ETFs have some good points.  They are cheaper than the average mutual fund.  But there are some bad points too.  You have to pay a fee for each trade, just like you do for a stock.  There are many ETFs to choose from.  It is a good idea for smart investors to check if the benefits of an ETF are real and how big they are.

We will look at the ETF IHF.  We will compare it to the top 10 stocks that are part of the ETF.  We want to see if owning one ETF is as good as owning the 10 stocks separately.  We also want to know if there is a better way to own these stocks.

To make it easier to understand, we will only look at the top 10 stocks that make up 63.58% of all the assets in the ETF.  These stocks are listed below with the percentage of the total assets.

We can use numbers to see how well the 10 stocks represent the ETF.  We will use a special method to calculate the Beta and Return if the 10 stocks were the only stocks in a portfolio.  The numbers are shown in the chart below.

The chart shows that the 10 stocks would give a 6.11% higher return than the ETF, a 16% increase.  The Beta of the 10 stocks is 0.12 lower than the ETF.  It seems that a portfolio of just the 10 stocks could give a higher return with less risk.

But we need to be sure that these results are real and not just a chance.  To do this, we will look at the standard deviation of each of the 10 stocks.  We will compare the total standard deviation of the 10 stocks to that of the ETF IHF.

Edgar Allan Poe wrote a poem called "Dream-Land". It is one of his best poems. In "Dream-Land", Poe uses the word "Thulé". He got this word from Virgil. Virgil used it to describe an island near Britain. The Greeks thought it was the edge of the world.

Some people think Virgil used the word first. But Poe may have also gotten it from a German writer named Goethe. Poe liked Goethe's writing a lot.

A man named Karl Arndt wrote a book about Poe and Goethe. Arndt said that Poe's poem "Dream-Land" is similar to Goethe's poem. Goethe wrote a famous play called "Faust". It is about a man who sells his soul to the devil. Part two of "Faust" has a short poem called "The King of Thulé". It is about a king who is sad because his wife died.

The king drinks too much and cries. He decides to die. He gives his things to his children and throws away his favorite cup. Then he dies. Poe's king in "Dream-Land" is similar to Goethe's king. Poe may have been thinking of his own sadness when he wrote the poem.

Goethe's "Faust" was made into a play in 1842. Poe used the word "Thulé" in another poem in 1842. Poe used it again in "Dream-Land". "The King of Thulé" and "Dream-Land" are like two poems that go together.

In "Dream-Land", the speaker talks about a place called Thulé. It is dark and lonely. He is scared and sees a world without color. Goethe's king in "The King of Thulé" is also sad and lonely. He lost his wife and wants to die.

Goethe was a famous writer. Poe probably knew his work. Poe liked another writer named Tennyson. Poe said he admired Tennyson. Poe may have read Goethe's work because of Tennyson.

In California, a customer who falls and is hurt can ask for more money in court. This is called punitive damages. The customer, Jennifer Palmer, slipped and fell on applesauce in a store. She thinks the manager, Paul Martin, did something wrong. He knew about the spill twice, but did not clean it up for 30 minutes because he was eating dinner.

A judge might not quickly throw out Palmer's claim. To win punitive damages, the customer must show that the store manager acted very badly. He must have known that his actions would cause harm. The manager knew that the store had many problems with people slipping before. Palmer fell at 5:30 pm. Before that, two employees told Martin about the spill at 5:00 and 5:15 pm. They said it was a problem, but Martin did not help.

The store had five other problems with people slipping in 2009. Palmer is now suing the store for money. She wants to know if the manager did something very wrong. In California, a person can get more money if the other person acted with "oppression, fraud or malice." This means the manager did something on purpose to hurt someone, or he acted very badly and knew it could hurt someone.

A court said that acting very badly means knowing that something will hurt someone and doing it anyway. The manager knew that not cleaning the spill could hurt someone. He did not clean it and someone fell and was hurt.

I took a course in Islam four years ago at CBC.  We talked a lot about if Islam is a bad religion.  I think this question is very important now.  Since 9/11, I have seen media in America change.  First, they were very negative towards Islam.  Then, they became very kind to Islam.  It's hard to believe that in 2001, an American president with Muslim family members could run for office.

I like the story of the Prophet Muhammad.  What I know about his history is different from what his story says.  I thought Muhammad forced people to become Muslim.  But his story says he was a kind and humble man.  People were drawn to him because of his teaching.  I find some similarities between Jesus and Muhammad.  One example is when Muhammad made food for 40 men and it was always enough.

I think the writers of Muhammad's story want us to see him as a kind and powerful man.  This makes me question the story.  It seems they are copying the good parts of Jesus' life and saying they belong to Muhammad.  I don't like this because it takes away from the real story of Jesus.

There are many stories in Muhammad's story that are hard to believe.  They are told by people who heard from other people.  This makes the stories seem less real.  I don't think these stories prove that Muhammad was a great man.

What bothers me most about this story is that it makes Muhammad seem like a perfect man.  But history says he was not a kind and gentle man.  I wonder if Muslims today know the real story of Muhammad.

Jesus lived a long time ago.  His teachings and ideas were soon left behind in the development of Christian thought.  Christian ideas changed over time and moved away from Jesus' original ideas.  This is a common trend.  Many people today are more open-minded and want to think about new ideas.  They are not influenced by old ideas that were taught to them.  People who hold to old ideas will not be able to stop this change. 

In the future, many people will learn more about history and will think about Jesus' original ideas.  They will want to know the difference between the ideas that were added to Christianity over time and Jesus' original message.  It will take a long time, but the result will be clear: Christian ideas will return to their original form.  People will remove old ideas, one by one, like turning back the clock.  The result will be a return to Jesus' original ideas.  This movement will grow and spread to many people.  The church will still be strong, but the people will be more united in their beliefs.

History shows us that changes like this can happen.  In the past, the Roman Empire persecuted Christians.  Later, the empire became Christian.  In our country, African-Americans were once slaves, but now they lead our country.  The same thing will happen in the Christian religion.  People will look back to Jesus' ideas and learn from them. 

To understand Jesus' ideas, we must read his words as examples, not as direct facts.  If we go back in history, we find the Jewish people.  They were the roots of Christianity.  They believed in one God and the authority of their holy writings.  The Jewish people had different groups, like the Sadducees, Pharisees, and others.

The Jungle shows how humans are naturally selfish. They only care about themselves and want to make their lives better. But they do not care about others. The book shows this in many ways. One way is with the owners and managers of big factories. All they want is to make their companies big and successful. They do not care about anything that gets in their way or gets hurt.

The book describes the factories as very dirty. There is a lot of smoke from the factories. The writer, Upton Sinclair, wants to show how the factories are hurting the environment. He says the owners do not care about people or animals that might get hurt.

The owners also do not care about their workers. They want to make as much money as they can. They make their workers work very long hours and do not give them any help when they get sick or hurt. The workers have no protection. The owners can fire them without warning and do not give them any money.

In the time when the book was written, there were no laws to protect workers. The owners could do whatever they wanted. They made their workers work very hard in very bad conditions. The workers were very poor and had no one to help them. They were like slaves. The writer says that the workers were treated very badly and had no way to escape the system.

The workers had no organizations to help them. The unions that were supposed to help them were not fair. They took money from the workers and did not help them. The workers were very unhappy and had no way to make their lives better.

The writer says that the workers were treated very badly. They were like slaves. The writer says that this is very sad and not fair.

Many writers use different methods to make readers feel a certain way about important things. Some methods work better than others. F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many of these methods in his book The Great Gatsby. He pairs words together in new ways to give readers a certain feeling. He also uses symbols to mean something and then uses them again to make readers think the same thing.

Fitzgerald uses this technique with colors like gold, green, white, and red. In his book The Great Gatsby, he makes people think about the meaning of these colors. He makes the colors white and gray mean the same thing - uniformity. White is a better, more upper-class color, and gray is an older, faded color. He shows this in the beginning of the book by using these colors a lot. 

At the beginning, many characters wear white. Daisy and Jordan wear white a lot. Even the wealthy Tom wears a white shirt. The only time they do not wear white is when the narrator goes to a party. Fitzgerald uses white and gray to describe ordinary things too. For example, he says the streets are "white chasms" and some people's names are "gray". He also describes ordinary people and places as white or gray. 

After showing the meaning of white and gray, Fitzgerald uses them to show that something is unimportant or ordinary. This starts with the character Daisy. He stops using these colors for a while, then uses them again to show that Daisy is just a regular person, not a special one. For example, he says she is dressed in white. He uses this technique again to show that Daisy is not a special character.

San Diego County is a good place for farming. The weather is not too hot or too cold. Many things grow well here. These include tomatoes, citrus fruits, leafy greens, squash, broccoli, herbs, peaches, lemons, berries, honey, and peppers. Many people want to buy food from local farms that do not use chemicals. They call this "organic" food.

There is a big market for organic food in San Diego. Many people want to buy food from local farms. Some farms in the area offer tours and let people walk or hike on their land. This is good for both the farmers and the people who want to visit.

Organic farming can have many benefits. It makes the land have more different kinds of plants and animals. This is because organic farming does not use chemicals. However, organic farming can be more expensive. Farmers need to work harder and use more labor to remove pests and weeds. They also need to use natural ways to make the soil healthy.

The land I chose for this project is in San Diego County. It is near a town called Potrero. The land is 160 acres and has chaparral, grass, and oak trees. It is next to a forest where many animals live. This land is in an area where many plants and animals are protected.

This land has been used for a long time. Native Americans lived here many years ago. Then, people used it for cattle and wood. Now, I want to help a farmer grow food and protect the animals that live here.

I looked at what the government can do to help farmers. I found a farm in the area that grows food without chemicals. This farm shows us what is possible.

Culture is very important in any negotiation. Culture is not just one thing. It is many things. It is not the same everywhere. We should not say "all Russians are stubborn" or "all Japanese are nice." These are not true. To understand a culture, you must understand what it means and how it works. When you meet a new culture, you compare it to your own. This can make it clearer.

To understand a new culture, you can read about its history. You can also learn about its problems. Instead of judging a culture, you should accept it. Then, you can work with it. This is especially important in a negotiation. If you are in a difficult position, showing respect for the culture can help.

Culture is not only about countries. Companies have their own culture too. This can be seen in how employees dress, how they talk, and how they work. Some companies like employees to work long hours. Others like a more relaxed schedule. Some companies want employees to help the community. Others do not.

Understanding what a culture values is very important. These values tell you why things are important to the culture. If a culture values being polite, a negotiator will not make a person look bad. If a culture values getting a good deal, a negotiator will not give up easily. Knowing these values can help you negotiate better. But it is also good to learn about the person you are negotiating with. This can make your negotiation more successful.

The Bible says, "There is no God." This is from Psalm 14. St. Anselm used this idea in his argument for the existence of God. Another man, Thomas Aquinas, also believed in God. Their arguments are similar, so we will begin with the idea that they are both right. This makes it easier to compare their ideas. If we said they believed in a different kind of God, we could not compare their arguments.

We will look at St. Anselm's argument first. He says we can know God exists by thinking about it. He says we know God exists because we cannot imagine God not existing. This idea is that we can know God by looking at what we already know to be true. Anselm says we do not need outside help to find the truth about God. We can find it in our own minds.

Thomas Aquinas has a different idea. He says we can prove God exists using reason and facts. We do not need faith to believe in God. This would be good for spreading Christianity because people could join the church if they understood the reason. Aquinas gives five reasons why God exists: change, cause and effect, things that are not necessary, degrees of perfection, and harmony. He says we can understand God's existence by using these ideas.

A long time ago, in the fifth or sixth century, a prince was born. He would one day be called the Buddha. He lived his life and became very wise. He taught people and his teachings helped create Buddhism. This is a very old religion, over twenty-five hundred years old. It has changed a lot since the Buddha lived.

You can see the changes in Theravada Buddhism in countries like Sri Lanka. In Sri Lanka, there is a special ceremony called the water-cutting ceremony. Many people participate in this ceremony, even those who are not monks. This ceremony is important to the people, but the Buddha never taught about it.

Buddhism is different now from when the Buddha lived. This is true for the Theravada Buddhist community. The community has changed its ideas over time. This happened because of forces both inside and outside the community.

There are special words we need to understand. An internal force is a force from inside the Buddhist community. An external force is a force from outside the community. A hostile force is a force that harms the community. A benign force is a force that does not harm or help the community, even if it does one or the other as a result.

First, we need to know the basics of Theravada Buddhism. Buddhists look to the Buddha, the Dhamma, and the Sangha for help. The Dhamma includes the Tripitaka, three groups of Buddhist texts. The Tripitaka is made up of the Sutta Pitaka, the Vinaya Pitaka, and the Abhidhamma Pitaka. The Sutta Pitaka has the Suttas, the Vinaya Pitaka has the rules for living, and the Abhidhamma Pitaka has the ideas about the world.

There are some important ideas in Buddhism. These ideas are Anatta (no soul), Dukkha (life is suffering), and Anicca (everything is changing). Recognizing these ideas can help end Sansara, the cycle of death and rebirth. If you become enlightened, you will not have lobha (desire), dosa (hatred), or moha (delusion). The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for laymen and monks. The five precepts for laymen are: do not kill, do not lie, do not steal, do not misbehave sexually, and do not take intoxicating substances. Monks have more rules to follow. The most important idea in Buddhism is the four noble truths. The first truth is that life is suffering. The second truth is that attachment causes suffering. The third truth is that suffering can be overcome.

The United States and Mexico had a long and serious problem for 57 years, from 1836 to 1893.  They did not get along.  The worst part of this problem was the Mexican-American War from 1846 to 1848. The United States won this war and got Texas and the American Southwest.

The two countries did not agree on many things.  They disagreed about their cultures, traditions and even religions.  America and Mexico also had big differences in what they wanted.  This is common between countries that share a border.

The United States and Mexico are not alone in having a long and serious problem like this.  Many countries that share a border have problems.  David M. Pletcher said that Mexico and Cuba have big problems with the United States.  This is because they are close to America.  Other countries in Latin America have good relationships with the United States.

A big problem between America and Mexico was their religions.  Some Americans did not like the Catholic Church and the idea of a king.  This caused a big divide between the two countries.  It was like the Cold War between the United States and the Soviet Union, but instead of being about politics, it was about religion.

The distrust between America and Mexico started from the time of their colonial rulers, the English and the Spanish.  This made it hard for them to get along.  Diehl and Goerts listed 17 disagreements between America and Mexico during their 57-year problem.  Most of these disagreements were about the border.  There were problems with bandits and outlaws on both sides of the border.

As time passed, Mexico became more dependent on the United States.  This helped to calm the problem between the two countries.  Finally, America's goals changed from wanting more land to wanting to help Mexico economically.

Fifteen years ago, I became very sick. I did not know the sickness was coming. At that time, I was a nurse. I chose to be a nurse because I wanted a safe job. Many people said, "You will always have work. People will always be sick." I wanted to be a scientist or a reporter, but I chose nursing.

I am now 46 years old. I do not have much money. I cannot work. I have been getting help from the government for 15 years. I do not have anything that is mine. Every day is hard for me.

I know one thing is true. I could not have made it without my family and friends. They helped me when I needed it. When disaster happens, you do not feel strong.

In life, big and small problems will always come. We cannot be sure of anything. We must be prepared, but some problems are too big to solve alone.

We need to help each other, not just rely on the government. We must learn to trust and help our neighbors. The idea of "rugged individualism" is not true. Our ancestors did not survive hard times alone. They helped each other.

We must prepare for disasters. I have a kit with medical supplies and food. I also have a flashlight, candles, and a way to purify water. If you have land and can grow your own food, that is a good idea. But it is also important to know your neighbors.

Organisms change over time. Why do they change in the way they do? Are there rules that control how they change? Many years ago, scientist D'Arcy Thompson said that it is hard to describe the shapes of living things using math. Today, it is still hard.

Recently, scientists have used math to study how mollusks grow their shells. They look at how shells grow from the inside out. They also look at how shells have changed over time. Our study is trying to understand how math can help us know how and why shells change.

We used special pictures of Prunum shells to find numbers that we can use in math. These numbers help us understand how shells grow. We used a computer program to create pictures of what shells might look like if they were different. This helps us understand how shells can change.

A shell is like a tube that grows over time. It grows in a special way. It makes a spiral shape. The spiral shape is made up of many turns. Each turn is called a whorl. A line that goes through the middle of the shell is called the columella.

Each whorl is separate from the next one. The line that separates them is called a suture. The biggest whorl is the last one. The other whorls are called the spire. The tip of the spire is called the apex. The other end is called the base. The animal comes out of the shell through a hole called the aperture.

We can look at shells from different sides. There are four sides: apical, basal, apertural, and abapertural. Most people look at shells with the aperture facing them.

To count the whorls, we look at the shell from the top. We find where the first line is. Then we draw a line to divide the shell in two. We count the whorls from this line. We can also estimate the number of whorls.

A shell is like a series of holes that the animal makes as it grows. We can follow the path of the holes. We can use math to understand how the shell grows.

We can use math to create a picture of how the shell grows. We can change the math to see how the shell might grow differently. This helps us understand how mollusks change over time.

Indonesia is not making fast progress in reducing the death rate of new babies and infants.  This is a problem.  Indonesia is meeting some of its goals set for the year 2015.  But it is not making progress in improving health for mothers and children.

Many new mothers in Indonesia now have a skilled worker present when they give birth.  This is good.  But this number still includes traditional helpers like midwives.  These helpers are not trained to help if there are problems during delivery.  This is why many mothers are dying from bleeding after giving birth.  The progress in this area is not as good as it seems.

There are also problems with helping children under five who are sick with diarrhea.  Not enough children are getting the help they need from a doctor.  We do not have all the numbers for this area.  But we know there is a problem.

Not enough mothers are having operations to help them give birth.  This is called a C-section.  The rate of C-sections is very low in Indonesia.  In cities, 7 out of 100 women have a C-section.  In rural areas, only 2 out of 100 women have a C-section.  This shows that people in rural areas do not have the same access to healthcare as people in cities.  This is a big problem.

Healthcare is not reaching all people.  Some people are rich and can pay for healthcare.  But some people are very poor and cannot afford it.  There is a big difference in the use of healthcare services between the rich and the poor.  This is not fair.

We need to figure out how to make healthcare better.  One way is to make a special program to help a certain area of healthcare.  This can help quickly.  But this can also cause problems.  It can take money away from other areas of healthcare.  And it can cause problems with supplies and paperwork.

Victorian novels are known for their detailed descriptions. They often focus on the rich people of that time. Two novels that are different from this style are Oliver Twist and Wuthering Heights. These novels use mystery and strange ideas to make the characters more interesting. This helps us understand their feelings and reasons.

The author, Charles Dickens, uses strange and confusing ideas in his writing. For example, one character heard voices and saw people talking to him. He was in a lot of pain and could not think clearly.

The two novels use mystery in different ways. In Oliver Twist, strange events help us understand Oliver's feelings and thoughts. Oliver had a hard time in life and did not know what was happening to him. He saw and heard things that were not real, like the sound of guns and people arguing.

One of the most important events in Oliver's life was when he was shot. He remembered this event many times, like a bad dream. He was very scared and did not know what was happening to him. The author wants us to know that Oliver had no control over his life and was very sad.

The author wants us to understand that Oliver was weak and did not try to control his life. He was very unlucky and did not know how to escape from his problems. This makes us feel sorry for him and understand his feelings.

The passage also talks about the way time passed. The day was very short and the night was very long. The author describes it as "long" because it was full of fear and "short" because it passed very quickly.

A few years ago, I worked with students after school. I helped them with their schoolwork, but I was good at English and reading. An instructor asked me to help a boy named Adrian. He was in third or fourth grade and had trouble reading. I noticed that something was strange. Some letters he knew how to say, but others, not at all. He spoke English very well, but I thought he might be from a different country. His mother did not speak English, only Spanish.

I helped take care of Adrian while the others went on a trip. His mother came in, and we talked in Spanish. I do not know much Spanish, but we managed. Then I understood the problem: Adrian knew how to read, but not the English alphabet.

I tell this story to show that language can be a big problem in school. Even if a child speaks good English, reading can still be hard. We can all agree that this is a problem. What can we do? In Adrian's case, we just needed to teach him the alphabet. For other children who do not speak English well, we need a better solution.

We have many ideas, but none of them work alone. We need to use them together. One idea is a dual language system. This is when children learn two languages at the same time. It helps them do better in school. Some people are afraid of this idea, but it is not true. If we use this system in all schools, all children will benefit.

How do we make this work? Do we need all teachers to be able to speak two languages? That is not practical. But we can have special helpers who are bilingual. They can assist the teachers in the classroom.

We are told from a young age that there is something bigger than us. People go to church, temple, or search for answers within themselves. We may accept the religion of our parents or reject it. Some people change their values many times. We search for a way to understand the world and ourselves.

One day, I asked my father about his favorite bird. We sat on our porch, listening to the rain. He looked out into the rain, thinking. He was very sick and thin. His hair was thin too. I felt sad and alone. I hugged him and sat close to him. We looked out at the rain together.

My father died in December when I was 22 years old. The doctors had tried to help him but it didn't work. I thought about God and why he let my father suffer. I said no prayers. If God was real, he wasn't listening to me. I didn't want to watch my father die. I wanted to remember how he lived, not how he died. I went to bed for three days and waited for the news.

Nobody called me to tell me the news.

The Gothic Novel is a mix of old and new ideas. This is what the writer Ian Watt says in The Rise of the Gothic Novel. People have many different opinions about the Gothic style. They say it has no real meaning, but some think it is very good. It shows a "terrible sublime" feeling that people like Edmund Burke talked about. 

The first Gothic Novel was The Castle of Otranto by Horace Walpole. He used ideas from old and new stories to create a new type of writing. He used old theatrical things and new ways to write about nature in his novel. This is what he called a "Gothic Story." 

The Gothic style uses things from old medieval theater, buildings, and traditions. Even when Walpole wrote The Castle of Otranto, the word "Gothic" was not just used for Gothic novels. It was used to describe many different things. People thought it was old-fashioned and not very sophisticated.

The combination of the old and new made the Gothic style last for a long time. It became old-fashioned, but also new again for readers who read it a long time after it was written.

One important idea in Gothic novels is the idea of chivalry. Chivalry is the way knights were trained in the Middle Ages. It is about being brave, honorable, and good. Walpole liked chivalry because it showed what a good knight should be like. He thought that people in his time did not live up to this ideal. He used chivalry in his writing to make the past seem more appealing and to show how people could be better.

Walpole wrote The Castle of Otranto during a time of trouble. He was sad about the future and thought that people in his time were not good. He wrote about a character named Frederic who is a prince and has many chivalric qualities. He has suffered and is supposed to be brave. This is an example of the idea of the "gallant and courteous Knight" that is often used in Gothic stories.

Supply chain management is the process of moving goods from customers to the customers. This process includes the stages of raw materials, making products, and delivering the products to the customers. The term supply chain management was introduced in 1982 by Keith Oliver, a business expert. He explained that supply chain management is the process of planning, making decisions, and controlling the supply chain to meet customers' needs quickly and efficiently.

There are six important parts of a supply chain: making products, getting supplies, keeping inventory, finding a good place, moving goods, and sharing information. Business managers use these six parts to give the best service to customers.

First, making products is the start of the supply chain process. It is the foundation for the whole supply chain process. The managers need to know what customers want. To know this, they look at the market. The market tells us what customers want. Once the managers understand customer demand, they decide what products to make and how many to make.

Next, the managers decide where to make the products. They choose the best place to make the products in a way that meets customer needs and keeps costs low. Then, they plan the work and fix any broken equipment. Making products is a very important step in the supply chain process. Every detail is important. If the details are not planned well, it can cost a lot of time and money.

The second part of supply chain management is getting supplies. This means making good decisions about the abilities of a company and its partners. A company may have many parts that make one product. Each part has different equipment, workers, and specialties. The manager decides which part is best for the different steps of making the product. Sometimes, a company decides to work with other companies to make the product. This is called outsourcing. Outsourcing helps a company be fast and flexible while keeping costs low.

A sign on a street says Hitler is alive in Burma.

Ellen Page, a famous actress, holds a sign above her head. The sign has an unsettling message. Burma is a country in Southeast Asia. A group of military leaders took power in Burma in 1962. In 2007, people protested in the streets. The protests were led by many Buddhist monks. These protests are called the Saffron Revolution. The monks wear yellow robes. 

At first, the government allowed the monks to gather peacefully. But then the violence started. The military hurt many people and destroyed monasteries. They arrested foreign journalists. A Japanese journalist, Kenji Nagai, was killed for being at a protest. The government says 13 people were killed. But a military leader says many more people were killed.

This is not new. Many governments have tried to stop people from saying what they think. It has been happening for a long time. Ancient Roman leaders thought they were gods. Japanese leaders think they are gods too. And our current president, George W. Bush, talks to a leader of a group called the Republican Party.

There are many examples of this. In 1989, people protested in China's Tiananmen Square. They wanted the government to change. The government says few people died, but others say many more died. In Rwanda, a group of people killed many others just because of their ethnic group. Many people were killed just because they were Jewish during World War II.

Duke Ellington's legacy in jazz music lasts because he was alive a long time and could make good music for many years. He could make his orchestra sound very good. 

Ellington plays piano in some of his songs, but as a composer, he made many complex and rich pieces. These pieces showed how good each band member is. He gave band members space to make up music freely. He also wrote music that was tightly controlled. This made each band member sound special. 

Ellington made the orchestra sound good as a whole. He made music that fit each song. He knew how each player sounded and how they worked well together. This helped him make very good music.

The Grove Music dictionary says Ellington made good use of voice in his music. He used voice like a musical instrument. This is seen in Creole Love Call. In Creole Love Call, Ellington used voice to make the music richer. 

Creole Love Call is a slow blues song with 12 parts. The song has 6 parts with voice and other instruments. 

Part 1: Voice and woodwind instruments talk to each other. The voice starts smooth and ends rough.

Part 2: A muted trumpet plays a longer version of the song. It emphasizes sad notes.

Part 3: A clarinet plays fast and high notes. The piano plays a soft and tricky rhythm.

Part 4: The whole band plays like Part 1.

Part 5: The reed section starts to talk, and the brass and rhythm sections play a new rhythm.

Part 6: The song goes back to Part 1. The voice sounds like a strong instrument.

The ending is short. It has a vocal run and a sad ending by a trombone.

Ellington made music that sounded good because he used voice in many ways. He used voice to make a rich sound in Creole Love Call. 

In another song, Hot and Bothered, Ellington made good music with a lot of instruments. A trumpet and a singer talked to each other in a special way. The singer sang like an instrument, and the trumpet played like a singer. 

In another song, It Don't Mean a Thing (If It Ain't Got That Swing), Ellington used a trombone player to make the music sound good. The trombone player played the main part of the song.

A woman felt something was missing in her life. She thought about this for a long time. She was 14 when it started. Three years later, at 17, she still thought about it. She wanted a person, not a thing. But she was not interested in any boys. Some boys liked her, but she did not feel the same. She often thought about what could be the problem.

Her family life was usually calm. Her parents were nice and peaceful people. They never argued with each other. They rarely argued with her. They wanted her to be independent. She was a happy person with a big personality.

Today was not a calm day. She heard a loud cry from the kitchen. She ran to the room and saw her mother on the ground. She was in pain. She ran to her mother and said, "Mom, what's wrong?" Her mother said, "Ow, sweetie, I need you to take me to the hospital." The woman took her mother to the car and drove her to the hospital.

At the hospital, she smelled bad smells and felt worried. But she focused on helping her mother. She took her mother to a doctor and called for help. Doctors and nurses came and helped her mother. They put her on a special bed and took her to be seen.

Her mother fell from a high cabinet while getting a vase. She was wearing a special stool, but it was too low.

This study was done to see if following a special diet, called the Mediterranean Diet, can help reduce the risk of heart disease and stroke. The Mediterranean Diet is a type of diet that is high in plant foods and low in animal products. It includes foods like fruits, nuts, whole grains, and fish.

Past studies have shown that the Mediterranean Diet can be good for the heart. These studies found that people who followed this diet were less likely to die from heart disease or stroke. However, they did not look at the risk of stroke specifically.

This new study looked at 74,886 women who were nurses. They all answered questions about what they ate over a period of 20 years. The researchers used these answers to calculate a score for how well they followed the Mediterranean Diet. They also looked at the women's weight, if they smoked, and other things that could affect the results.

The researchers found that women who followed the Mediterranean Diet closely were less likely to get heart disease or have a stroke. They also found that women who followed the diet closely were less likely to die from heart disease or stroke.

Over 20 years, the researchers found that 2391 women got heart disease, 1763 women got stroke, and 1077 women died from heart disease or stroke. Women who followed the Mediterranean Diet closely were 29% less likely to get heart disease or stroke.

In 2007, the United States had a big financial problem. Many people lost their jobs. The housing market also fell. Some big companies in America failed. This problem still exists today. We need to know why it happened and how to stop it.

The financial crisis was caused by bad decisions made by politicians. They pushed banks to give loans to people who could not pay them back. The financial system was not strong enough to deal with these loans. Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac had to help by making these loans into new investments. When people defaulted on these loans, the banks did not have enough money. They then gave their problems to others.

The problem started in 1999. The President wanted to be popular. He made rules easier for banks to give loans. This helped create the problem seven years later. A man named Steven Holmes wrote in the New York Times in 1999, “Fannie Mae was under pressure to give more loans to people who did not have much money. Fannie Mae wanted to make a lot of money.”

Holmes said the government might have to save Fannie Mae if there was an economic problem. He was right. The government had to save Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac in 2008.

Many things made the problem worse. Banks gave loans with rates that could change. They also made investments from these loans. This connected many parts of the economy to the housing market. People and banks borrowed too much money. When the housing market fell, they did not have enough money.

The housing market fell, and banks lost a lot of money. They had $4.1 trillion in loans in 2007. This was a big problem. Some banks failed, and others had to change to avoid problems. Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac had $5 trillion in loans and were taken over by the government in 2008.

Exposition is a bad thing.  It happens when you tell too much in a story.  You need to show the reader what is happening, not tell them.

You know the rule "Show, don't tell."  But I still forget to follow it.  Exposition is like a mean voice in your head that says, "Tell the readers about this, so we can get to the good parts."

Exposition is when you tell the readers what happened.  It is like a long conversation where one person tells all the details.  In a movie, this is when one character tells another person a lot of information.

For example, in a story, you are told that a woman met her husband at a certain time and place.  They got married and he was killed.  But that is not enough.  You need to know more about the husband and how he made the woman happy.  You need to see how much he loved her.  This makes you care about him and the woman.

A good writer makes the story interesting.  They show you the husband's personality through what he says and does.  This makes you feel sad when he dies.  It also makes you understand the woman better.  You see why she loved him.

As a writer, you need to add details to the story.  Don't just say, "They met, they married, he died."  You need to add flesh to the story.  It is like a chicken.  A chicken is just a chicken, but with meat, it is a delicious meal.

Don't be tempted to skip some parts.  For example, you might introduce a new character.  You know he used to be in the military and now he works at a gas station.  He has been married twice and likes to fish.  But that is not enough.  You need to show the reader who he is through what he does and says.

I watched two news programs from Columbus, Ohio. The first one was on NBC 4 this morning (August 13, 2011). It was a live broadcast. The main story was about a man from Ashley, Ohio. His name was Shad Hostettler. He stabbed his wife. The news showed his picture. He looked very bad. The news spent two minutes on this story. This was enough time.

The second story was about a young man named Travis Buyers. He was 18 years old. He was shot in the Sharon Woods area. He was very hurt. The police were looking for the person who shot him. There is a strong connection between brothers. This connection has many feelings: love, pride, anger, and sadness. Brothers understand each other very well. They see themselves in each other.

When brothers are in a difficult situation, their true feelings appear. These feelings can be good or bad. They can also bring big problems. To understand the feelings of brothers, we must see the results of their actions. 

When a brother looks at another brother, he sees himself. He sees himself, not how others see him. He sees his true character in his actions.

In a story called "The Scarlet Ibis," two brothers explore the connection between them. They travel through a beautiful place. They have strong feelings, including pride and anger. In a big argument, one brother is very disappointed. One brother lives.

The story shows us the feelings of the main character and his brother through what they do and say. It also shows us the feelings through the person telling the story.

The main character's feelings are all about pride. He wants a brother he can teach many things. He wants a brother to play with and have fun with. But his brother is weak and cannot play like he wants. This makes the main character feel sad and angry.

He even thinks about hurting his brother. But when his brother smiles, he feels happy and loving. This shows that he really loves his brother.

The human brain is a very complicated part of the body. It helps us learn and remember. Long ago, people did not know a lot about the brain. They compared it to a piece of paper (like a wax tablet), then to a special type of paper (papyrus), then to a book, and now to a computer.

Information comes into the brain from our senses. Our senses are touch, sight, hearing, and feeling heat. They turn physical things into signals the brain can use. The brain then uses these signals and makes new signals. It does this in two ways: bottom-up and top-down.

Bottom-up processing is like building a puzzle. It takes small pieces of information and puts them together. When you look at a picture of a black box on a white background, the brain puts together the colors and the shape to decide what you are seeing.

Top-down processing helps the brain understand things faster. It uses the information it already has to help figure out what you are seeing. In our example, top-down processing might help you know that it is a black box, not a hole.

The brain decided how important the information is and what to do with it. For example, when you walk, you do not see every blade of grass. But you can hear your name in a noisy room.

The brain stores information. There are different types of memory: what we see (sensory), what we are working with (working), and what we learned a long time ago (long-term).

First, the brain codes the information. This means it puts the information into a form the brain can use. There are special ways of coding for each type of information. For example, words can be coded by how they look, how they sound, or what they mean.

The brain must keep the information in memory. Animal studies show that working memory is like a short electrical signal that goes through the brain. Long-term memory is believed to be stored in special proteins.

There are many ideas about how the brain stores information. Some ideas come from how people remember things, some from computers, and some from the brain itself. One idea is that the brain is like a network. This network has nodes (or points) that are connected to each other. For example, the word "chair" might be connected to the word "table," which is connected to the word "wooden."

Aldous Huxley writes about a bad future in his novel Brave New World. People live in a place where the government controls everything. The people in this world value being part of a group above being alone. They are taught from a young age to be happy and not to question the government. 

The people in this world are like pawns in a game. They do not have the freedom to make their own choices. The government, led by the World Controller, tells them what to do. 

From a different point of view, called Marxist theory, Huxley seems to be saying that the government is bad. The people in the novel are not treated equally. Some people have more power and money than others. This is like a game where one group is in control and the others are not.

The government uses a trick to keep the people from knowing the truth. This trick is called false consciousness. It keeps people from understanding how the economy works. The people in Brave New World are not interested in learning about the economy. They are more interested in buying things and being happy. 

The lower-class people in the novel do not have the ability to make their own choices. They are forced to buy things and be happy. The higher-class people know about the government's trick, but they do nothing to stop it.

The people in Brave New World do not have real relationships with each other. They do not show deep feelings for each other. The only thing they care about is how others look. The novel shows that people in a world with a strong government and capitalism lose their freedom and individuality.

The people in Brave New World are content with their place in society. This is like what happens in a country with capitalism. The people do not question the government or try to change things. They are happy to stay in their place and follow the rules.

I am a student at University Park. I have been here for two and a half years. It is not easy to get around campus. Many people, including me, have this problem. My first year, I lived in a dorm in East Halls. It is far from the center of campus. I had to walk a long time to get to class in Willard building. It would take about 25 minutes. If the weather was bad, it was even harder. Now, I live off campus. I have to walk long distances to get to class in Thomas building. It takes about 25 minutes on foot. 

But I bought a bike. It makes my trip much faster. I can get to class in 5 minutes if I ride fast. However, I ride on a busy road called Pollock Road. It is not always safe.

Walking is another option. But I am too busy to walk. If I didn't have a bike, I would have to walk. It would take me 30-40 minutes to get to class. That is a lot of time. It would take me over two and a half hours a week. I don't have time for that.

The best way to get around campus is on a bike. But we need safe roads for bicyclists. My friend rides a bike too. He says it is the best way to get around. He is right. Bicycling is good for the body and it is fast.
